n your right- Drink the one on the right of the player who drew the card. 12- Fill/Drink Center Cup- There are a total of four 12s in the deck, the first 3 must fill a center cup with their drink, the last 12 must drink the cup with the drink mix. OK RULES PINGO //Pruebas DRINK ONE SHOT DRINK TWO SIPS HAND OUT 3 SIPS 1,2,3,4 WATERFALL SONGS BRANDS/LISTS DRINK ALL BUT YOU DRINK FROM EVERYONES GLASS DRINK THE ONE ON YOUR LEFT DRINK THE ONE ON YOUR RIGHT FILL UP/DRINK CENTER CUP
