//menu RULES Try to complete the highway. You will have to guess if the next card to come out of the deck is bigger or smaller than the card marked with the arrow to advance. But beware, if you make a mistake you will have to take a drink and back up a position (if the card is the same, it counts as a failure). The cards that are turned over are tolls, every time you pass over them you must drink, it does not matter if you have succeeded or failed, if you pass through a toll you have to pay it. You win if you complete the highway before the cards in the deck run out! Good luck! OK RULES
